name: Little Deer
description:
Super cute furry deer friends in a variety of poses. 

Collect a whole family!

Choose from:

Large stag looking forward - 15cm long x 14cm tall x 4cm wide
Large stag bowing down - 15cm long x 8.5cm tall x 5cm wide
Medium deer - 9cm long x 12cm tall x 4cm wide
Little deer looking back - 9.5cm long x 9.5cm tall x 5cm wide
Little deer head bowed - 11cm long x 7cm tall x 3.5cm wide
Baby stag - 12cm long x 13cm tall x 5cm wide
Baby doe - 10cm long x 10cm tall x 4cm wide

*These animals are replicas of real taxidermy, though the fur is real in most cases. The fur is either goat or rabbit and is a bi-products of the meat industry and therefore using a part of the animal which would otherwise be wasted. No animals are killed for the purpose of this product.
